CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 2, 1962, pg. 1, reads: "Happy Smiles of this group, pictured with Mr. Scranton indicate their satisfaction with their candidate. Top row (left to right) shows Warren Tessauro, Buford Holmes, Dave Thomkins, chairman of the Fifth Ward; Mrs. Millie Duncan and the congressman. Bottom row shows Joe Durzo, chairman of the 13th Ward and president of the fames '32' club, and Mr. and Mrs. John K. Tabor. Mr. Tabor was an unsuccessful candidate for city council. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Warren Tessauro, Buford Holmes, Dave Thomkins, Millie Duncan or Lillian Duncan Wright, Pennsylvania gubernatorial candidate William "Bill" Scranton, Joe Durzo, Mrs. Tabor, and John K. Tabor at Republican banquet in Loendi Club
